{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-certification-introduction/pinyin-to-hanzi-input","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Unos Pinyin za Hanzi","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Naučili ste već kako da unosite tačan Pinyin. Sada ste spremni da unosite kineske znakove. Ovde dolazi unos Pinyin-a za Hanzi. Pokušajte ponovo da napišete <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ni3 hao3</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">shi4 jie4</span> da vidite kako se \"Hello, world\" piše na kineskom!</p>\n<p>Ako napraviš grešku, samo obriši netačan deo i ponovo unesi.</p>\n</section>","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte zvuk i dovršite sledeću rečenicu.</p>\n</section>","explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Za unos Pinyin u Hanzi, možete napisati slova zajedno sa brojem tona kako biste direktno konvertovali u kineske znakove. Na primer, ovde, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ni3 hao3</span> se menja u <span class=\"highlighted-text\">你好</span>, a <span class=\"highlighted-text\">shi4 jie4</span> se menja u <span class=\"highlighted-text\">世界</span>.</p>\n<p><em>Napomena: Unos Pinyin Tona i unos Pinyin za sve Hanzi pretvara slova i brojeve koje ste uneli u Pinyin ili kineske znakove. Sistem automatski bira koju konverziju da koristi, tako da ne morate brinuti o tom procesu.</em></p>\n</section>","challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","superBlock":"a1-professional-chinese","block":"zh-a1-learn-certification-introduction","lang":"zh-CN","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-certification-introduction/pinyin-to-hanzi-input"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>BLANK，BLANK。</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"你好 (nǐ hǎo)","feedback":"<p>Ova reč od dve slova znači \"vesti\", kreirana je pisanjem <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ni3 hao3</span>.</p>"},{"answer":"世界 (shì jiè)","feedback":"<p>Ova reč sa dve slova znači \"dunia\", kreirana je pisanjem <span class=\"highlighted-text\">shi4 jie4</span>.</p>"}]},"inputType":"pinyin-to-hanzi","tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company1-reception.png","characters":[{"character":"Wang Hua","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_chinese_fundamentals_hello_world.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":5.18,"finishTimestamp":6.71},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":2.53,"dialogue":{"text":"<ruby>你好<rp>(</rp><rt>nǐ hǎo</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>，<ruby>世界<rp>(</rp><rt>shì jiè</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>。","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":3.03,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/#zh-a1-learn-certification-introduction","dashedName":"pinyin-to-hanzi-input","certification":"a1-professional-chinese","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a1-professional-chinese","chapter":"zh-a1-chapter-welcome-to-a1-professional-chinese","module":"zh-a1-module-introduction-and-certification-overview","block":"zh-a1-learn-certification-introduction","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-certification-introduction/how-to-set-up-the-chinese-keyboard-on-your-computer","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-certification-introduction/pinyin-tone-input","id":"691f071bd6a0ee105c5f571e","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":24,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-ce